how to take.
step 1 : install git on our armbian u can type "apt-get install git" (enter) answer y if need
step 2 : type git clone "https://github.com/analogipria/armbian.git" (enter)
step 3 : give akses to runing or u can type "chmod +x armbian/autoshutdown.sh.x" (enter)
step 4 : add script to cronjob u can take whith type "crontab -e" and add rule :
"* * * * * /(where u drop or downloaded file)/armbian/autoshutdown.sh.x"
pres ctrl+s and ctrl+x and taraaaa u script runing
